 in highgrowth corporations and expanding core businesses midmarket buyouts and divisional spinoffs  delisting of public companies whose market valuations are below fundamental values in order to allow for value creation through strategic managerial and governance guidance and private investment in public entities where they follow a valueadded approach including ma assistance and corporate governancetheir managers act as partners with their portfolio companies working actively with companies at the board of director level to provide financial and strategic guidelines while allowing management control of daytoday operations managing directorhead of sunrisejapan current clsa sunrise capital fund founded in 006 sunrise capital is a japan dedicated private equity strategy focusing on investments in established midcap companies sunrise capital supports domestic growth by providing strategic solutions for companies planning on asian business expansion our sophisticated management platform leverages our wide breadth of experience and extensive asian network senior manager prior the bank of tokyomitsubishi ltd new york branch the bank of tokyomitsubishi ltd provides commercial banking services the bank serves as the retail arm of the bank of tokyomitsubishi ufj btmu in the united states the company was established in 6 and is based in new york new york professional prior the carlyle group lp corporate private equity the carlyle group lp corporate private equity focuses either on a particular geography asia europe japan middle east and north africa mena south america subsaharan africa or the united states or a particular industry such as financial services the firm invests in aerospace defense  government services consumer  retail energy financial services healthcare industrial real estate technology  business services telecommunications  media and transportation boards  committees corporate boards ▾ outside director 0  current baycurrent consulting inc baycurrent consultin